    // ─── 28. G4F (GPT4Free) Local API (PRIMARY - KEYLESS ✅) ──────────
    // Self-hosted keyless aggregator. 1058 models, 30+ providers.
    // Verified working ✅ Returns responses through WeWordle, Pollinations,
